FBIS3-19979 "drweu058__a94025" FBIS-WEU-94-058-A Document Type:Daily Report 25 March 1994 ANNEX Italy & Vatican City Foreign Ministry Urges Nationals To Leave Algeria BR2403110994 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1752 GMT 23 Mar 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY BR2403110994 Rome ANSAMAIL Database Language: English Article Type:BFN [Unattributed article: "Algeria/Italy: Italian Nationals Urged To Leave"] [Text] (ANSA) Algiers, March 23 -- The Italian Foreign Ministry has asked the several hundred Italian nationals in Algeria to leave the country unless their presence there is "indispensable," diplomatic sources said here today. The sources said the "suggestion" was similar to the ones offered by France and other European Union countries through their diplomatic missions here.
